<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.3.2">
<l>empi rāṉē yeṉṉai yāḷvā yeṉṟeṉṟa laṟṟātē</l>
<l>yampiṉ vāyppaṭ ṭāṟṟa killā tintira cittaḻintāṉ</l>
<l>nampi yaṉumā cukki rīvā vaṅkata ṉēnaḷaṉē</l>
<l>kumpa karṇaṉ paṭṭup pōṉāṉ kuḻama ṇitūramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Indrajit, having not cried out again and again, “My lord, you rule me!”</l>
<l>Being unable to bear suffering arrowheads, perished.</l>
<l>Oh, Prince Hanumān, Sugrīva, Angada, Nala,</l>
<l>Kumbhakarṇa is dead and gone. Kuḻamaṇitūram!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
